{"word":"H2661 - חֲפֹר - chăphôr - khaf-ore' - Mole - மோல்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>חֲפֹר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chăphôr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaf-ore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Mole / மோல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"குழி, சந்து - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a mole (as digger)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H2658 - חָפַר - châphar - khaw-far'/2658\">H2658</a>; a <i>hole</i>; only in connection with <a href=\"#/H6512 - פֵּרָה - pêrâh - pay-raw'/6512\">H6512</a>, which ought rather to be joined as one word (shown as second form; by reduplication from <a href=\"#/H2658 - חָפַר - châphar - khaw-far'/2658\">H2658</a>; a <i>burrower</i>, that is, probably a <i>rat</i>): -  + mole."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2658 - חָפַר - châphar - khaw-far'/2658\">H2658</a>, <a href=\"#/H2660 - חֵפֶר - Chêpher - khay'-fer/2660\">H2660</a>, <a href=\"#/H2661 - חֲפֹר - chăphôr - khaf-ore'/2661\">H2661</a>, <a href=\"#/H2662 - חֶפְרִי - Chephrîy - khef-ree'/2662\">H2662</a>, <a href=\"#/H2663 - חֲפָרַיִם - Chăphârayim - khaf-aw-rah'-yim/2663\">H2663</a>, <a href=\"#/H6512 - פֵּרָה - pêrâh - pay-raw'/6512\">H6512</a>"}]}